#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.39"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.39:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.39:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga"
msgstr "4. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.39:0.3"
msgid "39. Paṭhamabrahmacariyasutta"
msgstr "39. The Spiritual Path (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.39:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.2"
msgid "“Brahmacariyañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, brahmacariyaphalāni ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the spiritual path and the fruits of the "
"spiritual path."

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the spiritual path?"

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.5"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the spiritual path."

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.8"
msgid "Katamāni ca, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaphalāni?"
msgstr "And what are the fruits of the spiritual path?"

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.9"
msgid "Sotāpattiphalaṃ, sakadāgāmiphalaṃ, anāgāmiphalaṃ, arahattaphalaṃ—"
msgstr "The fruits of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, and perfection."

msgctxt "sn45.39:1.10"
msgid "imāni vuccanti, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaphalānī”ti."
msgstr "These are called the fruits of the spiritual path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.39:1.11"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
